        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for information. Sclater was source of statement about <hi rend="italic">Numida ptiloryncha</hi> [as origin of guinea-fowl] in <hi rend="italic">The poultry book</hi> [pt 12 (Dec 1866): 288].</p> 
